Burlington to air freight for Wal - Mart Burlington Air Express said it has signed agreement with U . S . retail giant Wal - Mart to provide it with air freight services . Wal - Mart said it has selected Burlington to be its primary carrier for heavyweight export air shipments of time sensitive shipments over 50 pounds to its 197 international outlets . Burlington also was named secondary carrier for domestic shipments over 50 pounds . All international expedited orders emanate from Wal - Mart ' s Bentonville , Arkansas , headquarters . - Reuters Air Cargo Service Tel + 44 171 542 7706 Fax + 5017 - www . racs . com 
